    <descript>
      <abstract>This polygon data layer represents the surrounding region of the City of Alexandria, VA.</abstract>
      <purpose>This layer is intended for researchers, students, and policy makers for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a base map to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. This layer will provide a base map for layers related to real property as well as more advanced user applications such as urban and transportation planning, public policy, public works, or utilities purposes (including defining boundaries, managing assets and facilities, integrating attribute databases with geographic features, spatial analysis, and presentation output.)</purpose>
    </descript>
